      "start_time": 35.98,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Yeah, it's always busy just um, so I'm waiting to hear back from some of these agents to see, uh, which they want to do."
