      "start_time": 76.9,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "um, as far as the number of buildings right now it's, it's inventory even though inventory in the city is increased, my agents with their listings, they have only a few left."
