      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 116.52,
      "start_time": 115.07,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 29,
      "text": "So not that it's a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 123.18,
      "start_time": 116.53,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 30,
      "text": "It's just, you know, as I'm sure you guys know, I mean, it's uh you know, things have tightened up a bit loads of fun"
