      "start_time": 127.83,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 33,
      "text": "And you can definitely like rotate buildings around to, to your point if you want to have a few other agents kind of grouped in here as well too, just to help kind of get you a little more bang for your buck there."
