    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 183.04,
      "start_time": 182.26,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 48,
      "text": "Um,"
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 188.99,
      "start_time": 184.57,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 49,
      "text": "although, you know, listen, at the end of the day, I might end up just even though it's the same dollar amount."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 190.3,
      "start_time": 189.66,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 50,
      "text": "Um"
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 198.96,
      "start_time": 191.5,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 51,
      "text": "I just don't know if three months is gonna cut it to really give enough time to really see what kind of exposure, but maybe it will, I'm not sure you guys would know better than me."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 207.79,
      "start_time": 204.1,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 52,
      "text": "I mean, it really just depends on like the properties in the area, how the markets are looking."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 213.81,
      "start_time": 207.8,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 53,
      "text": "I mean, in some areas we can get vacancies in as little as a week, get filled in some markets and other markets."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 216.48,
      "start_time": 213.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 54,
      "text": "It does take kind of that couple of months to really get things flowing."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 218.53,
      "start_time": 216.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 55,
      "text": "This is kind of the benefit of this product though."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 221.63,
      "start_time": 218.54,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 56,
      "text": "It is meant to be more of an immediate lead gen boost."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 224.97,
      "start_time": 221.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 57,
      "text": "So typically that three months just help you get a better idea."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 238.53,
      "start_time": 224.98,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 58,
      "text": "Also from like the time management perspective, too of not having to like manage multiple listing contracts, not having to kind of go and have these conversations individually with multiple listing sites, it gives you that chance to kind of see those time savings as well too."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 243.91,
      "start_time": 239.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 59,
      "text": "And for us to be able to adjust around different sites that they're performing for your properties."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 244.24,
      "start_time": 243.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 60,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 245.18,
      "start_time": 245.16,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 61,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 253.3,
      "start_time": 245.19,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 62,
      "text": "And it's still listen, timing wise, I think, I think it's at least, uh, makes sense now because we definitely, uh, have seen a drop off"
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 256.09,
      "start_time": 254.33,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 63,
      "text": "in leads coming in."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 258.76,
      "start_time": 256.1,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 64,
      "text": "Um, just tied to seasonality, the holidays, all that."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 264.08,
      "start_time": 258.77,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 65,
      "text": "So, but landlords don't care, they don't want to hear that they just want their vacancies, they just want"
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 265.18,
      "start_time": 264.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "faf155d2-a48f-4404-9e2f-e338d98b3346",
      "order_number": 66,
      "text": "more, more people."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 266.48,
      "start_time": 265.19,
      "recording_attendee_id": "faf155d2-a48f-4404-9e2f-e338d98b3346",
      "order_number": 67,
      "text": "Uh, I in their building."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 270.64,
      "start_time": 266.57,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 68,
      "text": "Yeah, it's tough though because it's not just, you know, in certain pockets, it's across the board."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 272.33,
      "start_time": 270.65,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 69,
      "text": "You know, we're just really having a,"
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 278.88,
      "start_time": 273.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 70,
      "text": "it's November was and historically is the slowest between November and February."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 282.35,
      "start_time": 278.89,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 71,
      "text": "Those are the two softest rental months."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 285.89,
      "start_time": 282.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 72,
      "text": "But, uh, December, we usually pick up a little bit for 2.5 weeks."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 297.63,
      "start_time": 286.27,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 73,
      "text": "Um, but I would expect to have everything approved by, I mean, I'd love to say that I could get everything done by tomorrow, but I don't know if, uh, I'm gonna be able to get that done."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 301.05,
      "start_time": 297.77,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 74,
      "text": "Um, but definitely by next week and then get rolling."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 303.02,
      "start_time": 302.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 75,
      "text": "Ok."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 309.32,
      "start_time": 303.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 76,
      "text": "Well, the offer that we can hold until tomorrow was the delayed billing out to July or January 1st."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 317.8,
      "start_time": 309.33,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 77,
      "text": "And kind of the main benefit with that is that we can usually get these up and running within a couple weeks, you just get more time free by the earlier you sign is kind of the benefit of it."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 320.18,
      "start_time": 317.81,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 78,
      "text": "Uh, but we can definitely still hold that delayed date."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 324.22,
      "start_time": 320.19,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 79,
      "text": "You just won't get as much of like the free listing time in December."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 325.22,
      "start_time": 324.23,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 80,
      "text": "Does that make sense?"
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 325.52,
      "start_time": 325.24,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 81,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 326.35,
      "start_time": 325.53,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 82,
      "text": "No, that makes sense."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 326.76,
      "start_time": 326.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 83,
      "text": "Ok."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 329.25,
      "start_time": 326.77,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 84,
      "text": "Yeah, let me see how quickly I can get this done."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 337.79,
      "start_time": 329.6,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 85,
      "text": "Um, what and then once we, uh, get things, get the green light w what's involved on your end?"
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 343.78,
      "start_time": 339.97,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 86,
      "text": "Yeah, so it's pretty quick, all we would really need to do is just send this over via docusign."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 347.05,
      "start_time": 343.86,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 87,
      "text": "We get a signature and then it gets slotted into our implementation queue."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 352.14,
      "start_time": 347.06,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 88,
      "text": "So our team would just wanna set up like a 2030 minute meeting with you if you wanna have your agents on it as well too."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 353.34,
      "start_time": 352.15,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 89,
      "text": "You welcome to do that."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 365.02,
      "start_time": 353.53,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 90,
      "text": "Uh But it's mostly just to make sure we kind of get the listings live and get those up to date for you and walk you through that process, but it usually takes about two weeks on our back end to kind of get these listings live and good to go from there."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 368.65,
      "start_time": 365.17,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 91,
      "text": "And after that, you'll have a dedicated account manager that you can go to."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 375.76,
      "start_time": 368.66,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 92,
      "text": "If you wanna switch out different properties later on different buildings, that'll be kind of the go to person you reach out to, to help switch those out."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 386.26,
      "start_time": 375.77,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 93,
      "text": "But on that implementation call too, they'll walk you through how to access kind of the back end of rentable and track the leads, track the progress of your lead flow and be able to kind of see everything from your perspective as well."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 390.13,
      "start_time": 386.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "72ed751b-e550-4405-8f17-5d79a06cb166",
      "order_number": 94,
      "text": "So it's a pretty quick process once we get to the docusign process."
    },
    {
      "id": "699d0d83-8a1f-4e15-b332-f90228560ae4",
      "recording_id": "452457b9-680c-4756-8490-d422dbbc146b",
      "end_time": 391,
      "start_time": 390.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "585eb8d7-ed2f-4eb2-9504-79eba2a48141",
      "order_number": 95,
